2.5.name: wordpress/spatialmatch-free-lifestyle-search
2.5.description:
• SpatialMatch® FREE Lifestyle Search is a revolutionary lifestyle real estate search engine plugin for real estate professionals focusing on the broader lifestyle needs of a potential homeowner.

  • SpatialMatch® FREE Lifestyle Search enables the dream by allowing consumers to search for the particular area(s) that best match the hyper-local factors that impact the style and quality of life (i.e. the consumer "lifestyle").

  • Consumers can search for neighborhoods or communities based upon any combination of parameters relating to demographics, education, points of interest, neighborhoods, and more (i.e. looking for the micro communities in a particular area that are in close proximity to the right high school, favorite coffee shop, place of worship and grocery store(s) is critical to today's real estate consumer).

  • SpatialMatch® FREE Lifestyle Search plugin instantly improves your websites competitiveness. It d
